Rules Of Use

Content will be rated:

Extreme violence without blood: 15+ Violence
Serious violence without blood: 12+ Violence
Moderate violence without blood: 10+ Violence
Mild violence without blood: 6+ Violence
Extreme violence with blood: 18+ Violence Blood
Serious violence with blood: 15+  Violence Blood
Moderate violence with blood: 12+  Violence Blood
Mild violence with blood: 12+  Violence Blood
Sexual violence: 18+ Violence Sex
Nudity in sexual context: 12+ Nudity Sex
